  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Voice of the Wordless Atlas",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "来自无言的阿特拉斯的声音",
    "TraditionalChinese": "無聲的寰宇之語"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A seed of creation, a tiny drop of the infinity of the Atlas. This mere atom contains boundless noise, each tiny vibration the hopes and dreams of entire lifetimes.<br><br>Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to <span class=\"name name-special\">resonate</span> the seed, converting its waveform into the audible range.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚创造之种，源于阿特拉斯的无垠的渺小一隅。这枚小小的原子之中包含着无尽的声响，每一次细微的震动都代表着无数生命的希望与梦想。<br><br>使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>使种子<span class=\"name name-special\">共鸣</span>，并将其中的波形转化为可以听见的频率。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "創造的種子，一小滴寰宇的無限。這顆微小的原子中有無限的聲音，每次細微的震動都代表了一輩子的希望與夢想。<br><br>使用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 讓種子<span class=\"name name-special\">共振</span>，將其波形轉換為聽得到的頻率範圍。"
  },
